{
  "description": "Autotest config for poetry-monorepo-multipackage — Poetry monorepo with sub-packages declared via [tool.poetry.packages] include. Root has requests; service-a has requests+httpx; service-b has flask+click. Validates Mend discovers deps across sub-package manifests.",
